          "Against GUNS-HANDLE: MECHANISM is the mechanism itself (metal on metal — higher centroid, higher crest, shorter decay); HANDLE is the hand and holster around it (leather and cloth friction, softer, longer). Genuinely confusable, and many files contain both.",
